<plot>Performing by himself after having previously starred with female vocalist June Valli, Andy Williams hosted this new summer program which mainly featured him singing favorite songs. In addition to Andy, many other performers also appeared on the show, with the acts tending to run toward adult music rather than the newfangled rock and roll.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?540263</url></doc>
